{"tid":141294,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"致高登打手／五毛同埋最低賤既早洩","createTime":"2017-03-02T19:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T05:47:11.000Z","uid":17510,"like":34,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a1c943340fe39d3e2374ba90ab7f4d0c994e029","tid":141294,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:36:21.000Z","msg":"估唔到早洩到今時今日都仲係咁不知悔改<br />\n向到縱容你班手下胡作非為<br />\n<br />\n我地黎得LIHKG<br />\n一早係將自己身家性命交託左比連巴<br />\n我地絕對相信連巴唔似得早洩咁卑鄙無恥<br />\n<br />\n老老實實  如果你肯一早為BAM HKG+而公開地躹躬道歉<br />\n根本就唔會搞到今時今日咁樣既局面<br />\n<br />\n到左今日高登再無高登仔係閣下咎由自取<br />\n你以為打殘LIHKG我地就會返返去你個垃圾高登只係你夢心妄想<br />\n<br />\n2016年11月出得第一個LIHKG  <br />\n我地就有本事可以再出得到千千萬萬個LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實講咁多都無謂<br />\n我地對連尼住同望遠兩位巴打係無條件信任<br />\n當中既情義係你依啲反覆無常既小人唔會明白<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之一句到尾<br />\n我就點都撐LIHKG"},{"pid":"adcbfee19dcd29013dead6511190963b70b55072","tid":141294,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T20:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0300918082a98387bb185e9e0251b5c7a2a99f4","tid":141294,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T23:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dac676ca68bbd4609da6081750a382bf8bfe92","tid":141294,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T23:26:15.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n波台死出lihkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a51b3e4cd2c8469b31a3fefa758ec249247425","tid":141294,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T23:49:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母林早洩"},{"pid":"f236f0b2f3969fbf6454f22184d101fd549d4e1f","tid":141294,"uid":54995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T23:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /